        <abstract> 
<p>CD acknowledges that Patrick Matthew, in his appendix to <hi rend="italic">Naval timber and arboriculture</hi> (1831), anticipated by many years CD’s explanation of the origin of species by natural selection. CD was ignorant of the work. If another edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> is called for, CD will insert a notice to the foregoing effect.</p> 
        </abstract>
